      "description": "Build SQLAlchemy query from query structure",
      "docstring": "Build SQLAlchemy query from query structure\n\nThis implements a query builder that converts a user-defined query structure\ninto SQLAlchemy filters. Supports:\n- Multiple conditions with AND/OR operators\n- Bracket grouping for complex logic: (A AND B) OR (C AND D)\n- Negation (NOT) on individual conditions\n- Random subset limiting\n\nArgs:\n    org_id: Organization ID (for multi-tenant isolation)\n    query_structure: Query structure with conditions and brackets\n    experiment_id: Optional experiment ID (for \"not yet assigned\" default)\n\nReturns:\n    SQLAlchemy select statement ready for execution",
